Package org.flowable.engine.runtime

Interface ProcessInstance

All Superinterfaces:
Execution
public interface ProcessInstance
extends Execution
Represents one execution of a ProcessDefinition.
Author:
Tom Baeyens, Joram Barrez, Daniel Meyer, Tijs Rademakers
